 inverse Compton scattering was able to explain ${\\sim}80\\%$ of\nthe reported TeV flux, indicating that the X-ray PWN is a major contributor of\nVER J2019+368.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 May 2017 03:17:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-14"}
