l sinks for the wave energy reduces the efficiency of the\nnonlinear parallel cascade in torsional Alfv\\'en waves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 May 2017 09:15:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-09"}
